{"tid":598634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中學嘅高質搞笑事","createTime":"2018-03-19T16:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T16:52:32.000Z","uid":128204,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c5b53bdab0d31672092fc2f9506f8ed6760007","tid":598634,"uid":128204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"話說諗起以前中學嘅搞笑事<br />\n<br />\n我地班有位大陸落嚟嘅同學，我地都叫佢朱同學。<br />\n<br />\n咁有一日啦，因為自己唔太想落去小賣部買嘢食，<br />\n所以就問左呢位朱同學可唔可以幫我買啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：朱同學<br />\n<br />\n我： 朱同學，你係咪落去買嘢食？可唔可以順便幫我落去買二寶丫?<br />\n<br />\n朱同學：係丫，冇問題，二寶丫?<br />\n<br />\n我：係丫，唔該哂你!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>咁我係期望收到嘅緊係糖啦</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/001919_991e2c52da9467f24b587be14729eb0e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F001919_991e2c52da9467f24b587be14729eb0e.png&h=7eea4cea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">(到佢終於上返嚟)</span></strong></span><br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n朱同學：你要嘅怡寶丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/002145_2db960c8a0c365c56857d06e3af6097e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F002145_2db960c8a0c365c56857d06e3af6097e.png&h=19a62011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPs:好掛住你地呢班中學同學，識我嘅人唔好起我底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出嚟食餐飯最實際"},{"pid":"506af5af97e99a4b61e805e22591fc0b8ef75464","tid":598634,"uid":128204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bfed07f53702d808bdcfc4842a6567649fd15ff","tid":598634,"uid":128204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119fc7bb02b7c92afb4d72dc6192331c58388715","tid":598634,"uid":128204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dce37093d887dd42ff2da62c9cae0952ace894e","tid":598634,"uid":128204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c0c1603c0610d96e29bd290dbf2c5a14fb4b17","tid":598634,"uid":128204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:35:53.000Z","msg":"唔想比佢沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a284e745aab61d6c339952b96911cd270ce3995d","tid":598634,"uid":155404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:40:56.000Z","msg":"幫你推推啦。"},{"pid":"825583dafd26d58fe57eb64b64dd136dbd6d4d15","tid":598634,"uid":94524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:51:57.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"1e89421612fe63027994f06c94d2eb8bb816a301","tid":598634,"uid":59830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}